  <front>
    <title>Connection-less Lightweight Directory Access Protocol</title>
    <seriesInfo name="Internet-Draft" value="draft-ietf-ldapext-cldap-01"/>
    <author initials="L." surname="Johansson" fullname="Leif Johansson">
      <organization>Catalogix</organization>
    </author>
    <author initials="R." surname="Hedberg" fullname="Roland Hedberg">
      <organization>Catalogix</organization>
    </author>
    <date day="22" month="February" year="2001"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This memo describes modifications to LDAP version 3[1] to allow
transport of a subset of the LDAP protocol over connection-less
transport. The case of UDP/IP is covered in detail in this memo but
other transport layers are possible.</t>
    </abstract>
  </front>
